latestIgtvVideos.caption:
India against abuse
⚫ Social media is a platform to find motivation, entertainment & encouragememt. Also to show talent or art. It's time to raise voice.. if this cause has struck a chord with you as it has with mine, plz do sign the petition attached in my bio.. 
This is our active citizenship right and women's safety is a social responsibility. The time is now to choose a side! We can choose the path of safety or be mere spectators to the abuse our woman face online. Thank u @sayanigupta @jabeen_merchant @changedotorg @arti_raghavan for addressing and taking this initiative.
